OL,3,CNew police footage shows Vince
OL,4,CMcMahon's 100 mph car crash
OL,6,FNewly released police video shows
OL,7,Fformer WWE CEO Vince McMahon crashing
OL,8,Fhis Bentley at high speed.
OL,10,FThe footage, which shows the high-
OL,11,Fspeed car crash in Connecticut last
OL,12,FJuly, reveals that a state trooper was
OL,13,Fattempting to pull McMahon over at the
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,FMcMahon, now 80, was driving his 2024
OL,17,FBentley Continental GT at more than
OL,18,F100 mph on the Merritt Parkway when he
OL,19,Fcrashed in the town of Westport,
OL,20,Faccording to state police.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
