OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772193826
OL,3,CNew police footage shows Vince
OL,4,CMcMahon's 100 mph car crash
OL,6,FIn the video, police Detective Maxwell
OL,7,FRobins can be heard after the crash
OL,8,Fasking, "Why were you driving all over
OL,9,F100 mph?"
OL,11,FMcMahon replies: "I've got my
OL,12,Fgranddaughter's birthday".
OL,14,FRobins' dashcam video showed McMahon
OL,15,Faccelerating away, then braking too
OL,16,Flate to avoid crashing into the back
OL,17,Fof a BMW. The Bentley then swerves
OL,18,Finto a guardrail and careens back
OL,19,Facross the highway.
OL,26,@pD@IOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
