OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772193826
OL,3,CNew police footage shows Vince
OL,4,CMcMahon's 100 mph car crash
OL,6,FNo one was seriously injured in the
OL,7,Fcrash, police said.JMcMahon was cited
OL,8,Ffor reckless driving and following too
OL,9,Fclosely.
OL,11,FA state judge in October allowed
OL,12,FMcMahon to enter a pre-trial probation
OL,13,Fprogramme that will result in the
OL,14,Fcharges being erased from his record
OL,15,Fnext October if he successfully
OL,16,Fcompletes the programme.
OL,18,FHe was also ordered to make a $1,000
OL,19,Fcharitable contribution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
