CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772193826
OL,3,CNew police footage shows Vince
OL,4,CMcMahon's 100 mph car crash
OL,6,FMcMahon's lawyer, Mark Sherman, said
OL,7,Fthe crash was just an accident.
OL,9,F"Not every car accident is a crime,"
OL,10,FSherman said. "Vince's primary concern
OL,11,Fduring this case was for the other
OL,12,Fdrivers and is appreciative that the
OL,13,Fcourt saw this more of an accident
OL,14,Fthan a crime that needed to be
OL,15,Fprosecuted."
OL,17,FState police said Robins was trying to
OL,18,Fcatch up to McMahon on the parkway and
OL,19,Fclock his speed before pulling him
OL,20,Fover.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@dO]rD@OOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
