OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772193826
OL,3,CNew police footage shows Vince
OL,4,CMcMahon's 100 mph car crash
OL,6,FThey said the incident was not a
OL,7,Fpursuit, which happens when police
OL,8,Fchase someone trying to flee officers.
OL,9,FThey also said it did not appear
OL,10,FMcMahon was trying to escape - though
OL,11,Fin the video the detective suggests
OL,12,Fotherwise.
OL,14,F"I'm trying to catch up to you and you
OL,15,Fkeep taking off," Robins says.
OL,17,F"No, no no. I'm not trying to outrun
OL,18,Fyou," McMahon says.
OL,26,@wD@QO]yD@AOU
