OL,12,FMcMahon stepped down as WWE's CEO in
OL,13,F2022 amid a company investigation into
OL,14,Fsexual misconduct allegations.
OL,16,FHe also resigned as executive chairman
OL,17,Fof the board of directors of TKO Group
OL,18,FHoldings, the parent company of WWE,
OL,19,Fin 2024, a day after a former WWE
OL,20,Femployee filed a sexual abuse lawsuit
OL,21,Fagainst him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
