OL,3,CNew police footage shows Vince
OL,4,CMcMahon's 100 mph car crash
OL,6,FMcMahon has denied the allegations and
OL,7,Fthe lawsuit remains pending.
OL,9,FMcMahon bought what was then the World
OL,10,FWrestling Federation in 1982 and
OL,11,Ftransformed it from a regional
OL,12,Fwrestling company into a worldwide
OL,13,Fphenomenon.
OL,15,FBesides running the company with his
OL,16,Fwife, Linda, who is now the US
OL,17,Feducation secretary, he also performed
OL,18,Fat WWE events as himself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
